Introduction

Yunho is a South Korean dancer, singer, songwriter, and actor under KQ Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group ATEEZ, in which he debuted on October 24, 2018 with the release of their first mini album "TREASURE EP.1: All to Zero".

In 2021, Yunho debuted as an actor through the KBS Drama 'Imitation', in which he played the leading role of Yoojin, a member of the fictional boy group SPARKLING.
